{"tid":507577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好大既官威】珠江客船中途回航 惹接載內地大人物疑雲","createTime":"2017-12-23T11:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T14:12:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6045b383d5415e06a9f109b7e4bf966a1958410a","tid":507577,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/23/195128_6ce526918b5bd75ce04c19c4c10479f3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F23%2F195128_6ce526918b5bd75ce04c19c4c10479f3.jpeg&h=9316e2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珠江客運今早有船隻故障，導致船務需要作出臨時安排，有已離港的客船需要中途折返接客，結果引起受影響客船的乘客鼓譟，更惹來接載內地大人物疑雲。珠江客運一班由本港開往南沙港的客船，今早航行40分鐘後，突然在未有任何廣播下中途折返，引起船上大部份乘客鼓譟。有船上乘客稱，客船折返中港城後，有兩名疑似內地官員的男子，由船公司職員掩護下進入頭等艙，之後客船再度起航。<br />\n<br />\n乘客林先生稱，客船今早7時45分於尖沙嘴中港城開出，航行40分鐘後，有乘客發現客船竟然掉頭折返，但船上一直沒有任何廣播解釋原因。乘客得知客船回航後，即時鼓譟，有乘客立即離開座位質問船員回航原因，但職員表示一切由船長決定，他們亦不知道原因。<br />\n<br />\n林先生指，當客船返回碼頭後，船外有十多名操普通話的內地男子由船公司職員安排準備上船，此舉激起乘客不滿，有乘客擋著出入口與職員理論，但有兩名年約50歲的內地男子，則成功由職員掩護下進入客船，並被安排到頭等艙。林先生稱，幾經交涉後，除該兩名疑似內地官員的男子可成功登船外，其他內地男子最終無法成功登船，之後客船再度起航。<br />\n<br />\n據知，因早上8時許，有船舶故障無法使用，導致300多名乘客前往江門及斗門，船公司安排其他往南沙，珠海九州港，中山，廣州蓮花山及南沙港的船隻接載受影響旅客。珠江客運今日亦有在公司網頁發出相關通告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171223/57617113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F57617113&d=pg4RXjSvMZlgN6Im%2F0x5HMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=f4ed765e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171223%2F57617113&h=1e3b5e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171223/57617113</a>"},{"pid":"903447353a5c665054332c7a77edb72b4dc1dc69","tid":507577,"uid":71257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:54:30.000Z","msg":"官喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直升機都call唔到嘅垃圾官"},{"pid":"a35d0542731264eb8d8bc9399b9159c742e6d8b3","tid":507577,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"行咗40分鐘先折返? <br />\n個官又廢咗D. 直昇機都冇錢搭."},{"pid":"cb56c7c6535f7c3217d2390d41eedc4d19f26f34","tid":507577,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"不如直接就洗頭艇仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36509576b3a0cb92893babc3a652f1602f2dcf9","tid":507577,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a35d0542731264eb8d8bc9399b9159c742e6d8b3","tid":507577,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"行咗40分鐘先折返? <br />\n個官又廢咗D. 直昇機都冇錢搭."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"代表唔會浪費公帑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c753daf0df38f8c36fab8481e773fde3b506e3","tid":507577,"uid":19166,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-s14pDsx1Mvw/V4CHxtc6RDI/AAAAAAAAA8g/SSG6uKyEuA4re22bJZV5HRw7biKdBy0OACLcB/s1600/lyc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-s14pDsx1Mvw%2FV4CHxtc6RDI%2FAAAAAAAAA8g%2FSSG6uKyEuA4re22bJZV5HRw7biKdBy0OACLcB%2Fs1600%2Flyc.jpg&h=d58e5b11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a124cdcc4fa824086166c44c7e8b0c531f0f8907","tid":507577,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"再嘈下次用洗頭艇運你去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438b3fe2f5c2398c865e6b7cc1576abaee464e87","tid":507577,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"雜種平個支那夢成功的話<br />\n<br />\n世界黑暗時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff91724a3a999cc83fe31f8e